"title": "5263: communication",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5263: communication",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The effective conveyance of a message. God has communicated with humanity, especially through his Son. Christians are encouraged to communicate God's word effectively to others.</p>\n<h2>God communicates with people</h2>\n<h3>Through his creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:4\">PSA 19:1–19:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>Through the Scriptures</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:20-2Pet1:21\">2PE 1:20–1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:2\">JER 36:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:3\">EZK 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Through his Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:18\">JHN 1:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:3\">HEB 1:1–1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:9\">COL 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Through the human conscience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:9\">JHN 8:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:14-Rom2:15\">ROM 2:14–2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Through the providential ordering of life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:16-Acts14:17\">ACT 14:16–14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26-Acts17:27\">ACT 17:26–17:27</a></p>\n<h3>Through angelic appearances</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:11-Judg6:12\">JDG 6:11–6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:3\">JDG 13:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:9\">ZEC 1:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20\">MAT 1:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:11-Luke1:13\">LUK 1:11–1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:28\">LUK 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:9-Luke2:11\">LUK 2:9–2:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26\">ACT 8:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:1\">REV 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Through dreams</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:5\">1KI 3:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:1\">DAN 7:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Through visions</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:1\">ISA 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:24-Ezek11:25\">EZK 11:24–11:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:1\">DAN 8:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:1-Obad1:21\">OBA 1:1–1:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:3\">ACT 10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:9-Acts10:17\">ACT 10:9–10:17</a></p>\n<h3>Through a donkey</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:27-Num22:31\">NUM 22:27–22:31</a></p>\n<h3>Through miracles</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25\">JHN 11:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:43-John11:44\">JHN 11:43–11:44</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22\">ACT 2:22</a> <em>The miracles of Jesus Christ were not merely wonderful occurrences; they were also signs that conveyed spiritual truth.</em></p>\n<h2>God has communicated directly with individuals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:2-Exod3:6\">EXO 3:2–3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:9\">EXO 33:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:21\">EXO 33:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:12-1Kgs19:13\">1KI 19:12–19:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ and communication</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ communicated his Father's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:49\">JHN 12:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9-John14:10\">JHN 14:9–14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:24\">JHN 14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:15\">JHN 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:8\">JHN 17:8</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ used parables in order to communicate with some but not with others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:10-Mark4:12\">MRK 4:10–4:12</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:10-Matt13:15\">MAT 13:10–13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:9-Luke8:10\">LUK 8:9–8:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:9-Isa6:10\">ISA 6:9–6:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:39\">JHN 9:39</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit and communication</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:15\">JHN 16:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8\">JHN 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:16\">ROM 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:24\">1JN 3:24</a></p>\n<h2>Christians are to communicate the good news to other people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46-Luke24:48\">LUK 24:46–24:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:7\">MAT 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:19–28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:12\">MRK 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:15\">MRK 16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:20\">MRK 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:20\">ACT 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:27\">ACT 20:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:17-Acts26:20\">ACT 26:17–26:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:14-Rom10:15\">ROM 10:14–10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:8\">1TH 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>The failure of communication</h2>\n<h3>Inadequate perception of the truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:16-Mark8:21\">MRK 8:16–8:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:13\">MRK 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:10\">JHN 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:27\">JHN 8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:6\">JHN 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:22\">JHN 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:18\">JHN 16:18</a></p>\n<h3>Wilful rejection of the truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:18\">EPH 4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:47\">JHN 8:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21-Rom1:25\">ROM 1:21–1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12-Heb3:13\">HEB 3:12–3:13</a></p>",
